{"text_id":16189,"tokens":["This"," work"," investigates"," the"," construction"," of"," central"," schemes"," for"," hyperbolic"," conservation"," laws"," with"," source"," terms","."," We"," address"," the"," issues"," of"," monoton","icity",","," stability",","," and"," convergence"," of"," these"," schemes",".","\n\n","Our"," approach"," involves"," a"," rigorous"," mathematical"," analysis"," of"," the"," scheme","'","s"," properties",","," utilizing"," techniques"," from"," operator"," theory"," and"," functional"," analysis","."," We"," establish"," necessary"," and"," sufficient"," conditions"," for"," monoton","icity"," and"," stability"," of"," the"," central"," scheme","."," Subsequently",","," we"," provide"," a"," constructive"," algorithm"," for"," obtaining"," convergent"," central"," schemes"," by"," trunc","ating"," the"," source"," terms"," appropriately",".","\n\n","Our"," results"," demonstrate"," that"," the"," proposed"," central"," schemes"," inherit"," desirable"," properties"," from"," the"," underlying"," conservation"," law",","," even"," in"," the"," presence"," of"," source"," terms","."," Applications"," of"," our"," schemes"," include"," numerical"," simulations"," of"," various"," hyperbolic"," models"," arising"," in"," engineering",","," physics",","," and"," applied"," sciences",".","\n\n","Keywords",":"," Hyper","bolic"," conservation"," laws",";"," Central"," schemes",";"," Mon","oton","icity",";"," Stability",";"," Source"," terms","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"gemma-7b-it","label":1}